{"id": "1442974019421863987", "channel_id": "1442961773060690112", "type": 0, "author_id": "1298268532017991702", "author_name": "sweet_25367", "author_bot": false, "content": "+12榜单哈姆林为什么会在那里  \n同样满灵塑情况下：  \n70级哈姆林丢一张灵感21临力，一张追忆9永力  \n80级哈姆林丢一张灵感23临力，一张追忆9永力（……）  \n90级哈姆林丢一张灵感25临力，一张追忆10永力", "timestamp": "2025-11-25T20:23:35.391000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-25T20:27:12.253000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1442961773060690112", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "2.4 角色命轮榜单", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748", "1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174180524034637854", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1442974573934018620", "channel_id": "1442961773060690112", "type": 0, "author_id": "1298268532017991702", "author_name": "sweet_25367", "author_bot": false, "content": "我想象不到有什么队伍会需要为了10临力，一回合最多多长4永力把哈姆林抽到+12  <:processing:1357185814567718963>   \n~~不如捡个寂静序曲~~\n哦还有他人格深化给的暴击，主c输出回合暴击溢出，辅助技能没有和暴击联动，相当于给了个没有任何用的属性", "timestamp": "2025-11-25T20:25:47.597000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-25T20:38:08.241000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1442961773060690112", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "2.4 角色命轮榜单", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748", "1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174180524034637854", "1174179700470460447"]}
